snippet.title: Powerpuff Girls Chemical X-traction Story Part 1
snippet.description: Created for the PS1 game. by David Moss in 2001. This was the first part of the games story that you saw at the beginning of the game. The story is pretty rubbish, but it came direct from Cartoon Network so I just had to work with what I was given.
